                span(style="display:none;font-size:20px;left:10%;top:80%" parent="socialtext1")
                    |MOMENTS
                span(class="socialtext2")
                    strong
                        |GAMING
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:47%;top:10%" parent="socialtext2")
                    |FANTASY
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:35%;top:10%" parent="socialtext2")
                    |CHALLENGE
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:59%;top:10%" parent="socialtext2")
                    |FICTION
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:43%;top:90%" parent="socialtext2")
                    |COMMUNITY
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:31%;top:90%" parent="socialtext2")
                    |STORYTELLING
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:54%;top:90%" parent="socialtext2")
                    |STRATEGY
                span(class="socialtext3")
                    strong
                        |FACEBOOK
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:74%;top:10%" parent="socialtext3")
                    |EVENTS
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:67%;top:90%" parent="socialtext3")
                    |FRIENDS
                span(style="display:none;font-size:17px;left:85%;top:70%" parent="socialtext3")
                    |CHAT
                img(src="/images/social1.png")
            div(id="work" class="clickable")
                img(src="/images/work.png")
            div(id="other" class="clickable")
                img(src="/images/social2.png")
        div(class="scrollarea")
            div(class="all")
                div(class="leftscroll all")
                    div(class="scrolltext")
                        |ABOUT ME
                div(class="midscroll all")
                    div(id="aboutme_click" class="clickable zoomhover")
                        img(src="/images/thumbnail_me.png")
                div(class="rightscroll all")
                    div(style="scrolltext")
                        |I am a Brazillian computer engineer who has been involved in the programming world for the past 9 years.
                        br
                        br
                        |I have the spirit of an adventurer and I want to try everything even if I may fail
            div(class="all")
                div(class="leftscroll all")
                    div(class="scrolltext")
                        |EDUCATION
                div(class="midscroll all")
                    div(id="education_click" class="clickable zoomhover")
                        img(src="/images/thumbnail_utfpr.png")
                div(class="rightscroll all")
                    div(style="scrolltext")
                        |I have graduated in Brazil's Technology University of Paraná as a Computer Engineer in 2012, a well-known federal university.
                        br
                        br
                        |What have I learned? A good developer knows how to implement solutions to problems, rather than simply create code.
            div(class="all")
                div(class="leftscroll all")
                    div(class="scrolltext")
                        |WORK
                div(class="midscroll all")
                    div(id="work_click" class="clickable zoomhover")
                        img(src="/images/work_thumbnail.png")
                div(class="rightscroll all")
                    div(style="scrolltext")
                        |I have joined ExxonMobil in 2012 as a full time employee and have been working with them since. I started as a tools developer within Customer Services department, with my time split between frontline customer handling and C# tools development to enhance department processes and increase efficiency
                        br
                        br
                        |Soon after I was assigned as a full time tools developer and I had the chance to work with initiatives that automated several manual processes in the company, such as new user creation, automatic analyst metrics (with SQL database & tableau) and some web (HTML and ASP .NET) development.
                        br
                        br
                        |Currently, I am developing software automations using BMC Atrium Orchestrator interacting with several technologies such as Unix/Centrify, PowerShell, ITSM Remedy/SRM and more. I am getting familiar with XML/XSLT, SOAP, REST and web services in general.
            div(class="all")
                div(class="leftscroll all")
                    div(class="scrolltext")
                        |INTERESTING?
                div(class="midscroll all")
                div(class="rightscroll all")
                    div(style="scrolltext")
                        |Scroll down!
    div(id="bottom")